://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Surf_%27n%27_Turf\" title=\"Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf\"><img alt=\"Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Surf_%27n%27_Turf.png?eef558\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/64px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meats\" title=\"Monster Meats\"><img alt=\"Monster Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meats.png?c5a3b6\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shark_Fin\" title=\"Shark Fin\"><img alt=\"Shark Fin.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Shark_Fin.png?d7a250\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limpets\" title=\"Limpets\"><img alt=\"Limpets.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Limpets.png?c18778\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Surf_%27n%27_Turf\" title=\"Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf\"><img alt=\"Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Surf_%27n%27_Turf.png?eef558\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrec