iv class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dead_Dogfish\" title=\"Dead Dogfish\"><img alt=\"Dead Dogfish.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dead_Dogfish.png?aa071a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mussel\" title=\"Mussel\"><img alt=\"Mussel.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Mussel.png?593d20\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Surf_%27n%27_Turf\" title=\"Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf\"><img alt=\"Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Surf_%27n%27_Turf.png?eef558\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/64px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Exchange\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dubloons\" title=\"Dubloons\"><img alt=\"Dubloons.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dubloons.png/32px-Dubloons.png?5bbf28\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Exchange</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Surf_%27n%27_Turf\" title=\"Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf\"><img alt=\"Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Surf_%27n%27_Turf.png?eef558\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Yaarctopus_Icon\" title=\"Yaarctopus Icon\"><img alt=\"Yaarctopus Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Yaarctopus_Icon.png/42px-Yaarctopus_Icon.png?9466be\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Boat_Lantern\" title=\"Boat Lantern\"><img alt=\"Boat Lantern.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Boat_Lantern.png?3d361e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/64px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf was introduced to <i>Don&#x27;t Starve Together</i> in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Return_of_Them#Version_History\" title=\"Return of Them\">Hook, Line, and Inker</a></i> update.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surf_and_turf\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Surf and turf\">Surf and turf</a> is a meal that combines seafood with meat, typically beef steak and lobster.</li>\n<li>Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf is also present in <i>Oxygen Not Included</i>, another game developed by Klei Entertainment.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Surf_%27n%27_Turf_128x128.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\"><img alt=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Surf_%27n%27_Turf_128x128.png/120px-Surf_%27n%27_Turf_128x128.png?f80597\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Surf_%27n%27_Turf#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Surf_%27n%27_Turf#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
