  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf là ​​một Vật phẩm Thịt đi kèm với DLC Shipwrecked (hiện có sẵn trong Don&#x27;t Starve Together). Nó được nấu trong Nồi Hầm bằng cách thêm bất kỳ Thịt và Cá nào có tổng giá trị Cá/Hải sản là 1,5 trở lên và tổng giá trị Thịt của tất cả nguyên liệu là 2,5 trở lên. Do yêu cầu cao nên công thức này yêu cầu sử dụng Wobster, có giá trị cá là 2 hoặc sử dụng ít nhất một thành phần có cả giá trị cá và thịt, chẳng hạn như Cá nhiệt đới, Cá, Cá chó, Vây cá mập, Cá sống, Lươn hoặc Cá kiếm, tất cả đều có giá trị cá là 1 và giá trị thịt là 0,5…</p>",
  "title": "Surf 'n' Turf",
  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Exclusivity|Shipwrecked|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|canBeBurned=1\n|foodType = [[Food Type#Meat|Meat]] {{Pic|32px|Meats|Food Type#Meat}}\n|foodRecipe = {{Pic|32px|Meats}}x2.5 {{Pic|32px|Fishes}}x1.5 \n|icon = Surf 'n' Turf.png\n|image = Surf 'n' Turf Dropped.png\n|hpRestored     = 60\n|hungerRestored = 37.5\n|sanityRestored = 33\n|cooktime       = 20 sec\n|priority       = 30\n|spoil          = 10 Days\n|stack          = 40\n|spawnCode      = \"surfnturf\"\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = It's perf!\n|willow = Ugh. This is old person food!\n|wolfgang = Very good.\n|wendy = It could be worse.\n|wx78 = PREPARE FOR CALORIC INTAKE\n|wickerbottom = The perfect dish.\n|woodie = Good eating, that.\n|maxwell = A very balanced meal, I suppose.\n|wagstaff = There is a lot of meat based protein in this concoction.\n|wigfrid = Nothing goes better with meat than more meat!\n|webber = Eww, healthy!\n|walani = Can I eat it on my surfboard?\n|warly = Mwah! Perfection.\n|woodlegs = 'Could use wit less turf.\n|wilba = 'TIS A FEAST O' THE SEA\n|wormwood = Fills belly\n|wheeler = A feast before adventuring.\n|winona = Now THAT'S a meal!\n|wortox = My my, what an odd pair!\n|wurt = Blegh! Don't want it!\n|walter = So filling!\n|wanda = Perfect for people who can't make up their mind.\n|choose = wickerbottom\n}}\n'''Surf 'n' Turf''' is a [[Meats|Meat]] [[item]] bundled with the ''[[Don't Starve: Shipwrecked|Shipwrecked]]'' DLC (now available in ''Don't Starve Together''). It is cooked in the [[Crock Pot]] by adding any Meats and [[Fishes]] with a total [[Crock Pot#Food values|Fish/Seafood value]] of 1.5 or higher and a total [[Crock Pot#Food values|Meat value]] of all the ingredients of 2.5 or higher. Because of the high requirements, this recipe requires either using a [[Wobster]], which has fish value of 2, or using at least one ingredient that has both fish and meat values, such as [[Tropical Fish]], [[Fish]], [[Dogfish]], [[Shark Fin]], [[Raw Fish]], [[Eel]], or [[Swordfish]], all of which have a fish value of 1 and meat value of 0.5. Multiple [[Monster Meat]]s can be used in the recipe (as long as the recipe requirements are met) without the fear of making [[Monster Lasagna]], since Surf 'n' Turf recipe has a higher priority than Monster Lasagna.\n\nSurf 'n' Turf restores 60 {{Hp}}, 37.5 {{Hunger}}, and 33 {{Sanity}}. It takes 20 seconds to cook and can be given to the [[Yaarctopus]] in exchange for a [[Boat Lantern]].\n\nIn normal ''Don't Starve'' and ''[[Reign of Giants]]'' Worlds that are compatible with the ''Shipwrecked'' DLC, Surf 'n' Turf can be cooked using 2 Monster Meats and 2 [[Fish]] or [[Eel]]s. This meal can be somewhat easily cooked and consumed in the [[Caves]] or [[Ruins]] to keep Health, Hunger, and Sanity in check.\n\n== Prerequisites ==\n* Requires:[[File:Meats Crock Pot.png|link=Meats]]\n* Requires:[[File:Fishes Crock Pot.png|link=Fishes]]\n* Excludes:[[File:Ice.png|link=Ice]]\n\n== [[File:Cookbook.png|32px|link=]] Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Meats\n|count1 = 2.5\n|item2 = Fishes\n|count2 = 1.5\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Surf 'n' Turf\n|comparator1=&times;|comparator2=&times;}}\n\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Monster Meats\n|item2 = Fish\n|count2 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Surf 'n' Turf\n|item=Monster Meats|count=2}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Monster Meats\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Raw Fish\n|count2 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Surf 'n' Turf\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Monster Meats\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Eels\n|count2 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Surf 'n' Turf\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Normal Meats\n|item2 = Meats\n|item3 = Fishes\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Surf 'n' Turf\n|dlc = Shipwrecked\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Monster Meats\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Roe\n|item3 = Limpets\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Surf 'n' Turf\n|dlc = Shipwrecked\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Monster Meats\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Wobster\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Surf 'n' Turf\n|dlc = Shipwrecked\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Monster Meats\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Shark Fin\n|item3 = Limpets\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Surf 'n' Turf\n|dlc = Shipwrecked\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Monster Meats\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Dead Dogfish\n|item3 = Fish Morsel\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Surf 'n' Turf\n|dlc = Shipwrecked\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Meat\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Dead Dogfish\n|item3 = Mussel\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Surf 'n' Turf\n|dlc = Shipwrecked\n}}\n\n=={{Pic32|Dubloons}} Exchange ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Surf 'n' Turf\n|tool = Yaarctopus Icon\n|result = Boat Lantern\n|dlc = Shipwrecked\n}}\n\n== {{Pic32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n* Surf 'n' Turf was introduced to ''Don't Starve Together'' in the ''[[Return of Them#Version History|Hook, Line, and Inker]]'' update.\n* [[Wikipedia:Surf_and_turf|Surf and turf]] is a meal that combines seafood with meat, typically beef steak and lobster.\n*Surf 'n' Turf is also present in ''Oxygen Not Included'', another game developed by Klei Entertainment.\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery>\nSurf 'n' Turf 128x128.png|Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\n</gallery>\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n[[Vi:Surf 'n' Turf]]\n[[fr:Terre et mer]]\n[[ru:Жаркое]]\n__NOTOC__\n[[Category:Food]]\n[[Category:Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]\n[[Category:Healing]]\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]"
}
